sile-launched-from-iran-ew-1205p-975fb4.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Eyad Baba</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Image: A missile launched from Iran in the sky, viewed from the Bureij camp for Palestinian refugees in the central Gaza Strip</media:text><media:description type="plain">People stand next to an unexploded Iranian missile on March 4 in Qamishli, Syria.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-03/260304-missile-Qamishli-International-Airport-rs-d87307.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:21:41 GMT</pubDate><title>Iran is accelerating efforts to dig out missiles and munitions</title><updateDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:21:41 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:25:56 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The Justice Department released chilling new surveillance video of the man charged with trying to assassinate President Donald Trump at the White House Correspondents’ Dinner. Prosecutors say it shows Cole Allen casing the Washington Hilton the day before the attack. New evidence photos also show bags of ammunition inside his room as well as a gas mask and protective glasses. NBC’s Gabe Gutierrez reports for TODAY.</description><expires>2056-05-01T11:25:06.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/doj-releases-new-video-of-assassination-suspect-casing-hotel-262516293652</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>DOJ Releases New Video of Assassination Suspect &#39;Casing&#39; Hotel</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/doj-releases-new-video-of-assassination-suspect-casing-hotel-262516293652"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777634697864_tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501_S3_1920x1080-428tqn.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The Justice Department released chilling new surveillance video of the man charged with trying to assassinate President Donald Trump at the White House Correspondents’ Dinner. Prosecutors say it shows Cole Allen casing the Washington Hilton the day before the attack. New evidence photos also show bags of ammunition inside his room as well as a gas mask and protective glasses. NBC’s Gabe Gutierrez reports for TODAY.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777634697864_tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777634697864_tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777634697864_tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501_S3_1920x1080-428tqn.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:25:04 GMT</pubDate><title>DOJ Releases New Video of Assassination Suspect &#39;Casing&#39; Hotel</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:25:56 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Jonathan Allen</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:00:41 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Sen. Elizabeth Warren, D-Mass., plans to campaign for Iowa Senate candidate Zach Wahls this month, adding firepower to a raging battle between progressive outsider candidates and the Democratic Party establishment</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politic