 a hat, pin, t-shirt and stickers.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Hundreds of 8647 products are for sale online on Amazon, Etsy and other retailers.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260430-8646-shirts-mn-0840-c0d7eb.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="302" width="492"><media:credit></media:credit><media:text type="plain">8646 shirts available on Amazon.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Hundreds of 8647 products are for sale online on Amazon, Etsy and other retailers.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-8647-merchandise-cs-c2792a.jpg" height="1600" width="2400"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 09:00:40 GMT</pubDate><title>&#39;Arrest us all,&#39; says Congressional candidate who sells and wears &#39;8647&#39; merch</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 10:56:55 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Yuliya Talmazan</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:09:27 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The Black Sea isn’t meant to be this black</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/russia/russia-ukraine-war-environmental-disaster-toxic-fumes-rcna342663</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/russia/russia-ukraine-war-environmental-disaster-toxic-fumes-rcna342663</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260429-tuapse-mb-1552-020e15.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1676" width="2500"><media:credit>Boris Morozov</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Russia Oil Refinery Fire</media:text><media:description type="plain">A large plume of thick smoke from a Ukrainian drone attack on an ⁠oil refinery in the Black Sea port ⁠of Tuapse, Russia on April 28, 2026.</media:description></media:content><media: